{"tid":346443,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男人係咪鍾意比人虐待","createTime":"2017-08-04T03:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T14:04:07.000Z","uid":32797,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b092cdf05ab89997ed41827cfdab4cb3e7eaf1f3","tid":346443,"uid":32797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:19:14.000Z","msg":"男人都唔鍾意人對佢好，鍾意比人虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一個ex話我成日咩都無所謂，去邊食飯去邊玩都無所謂，叫我學下啲港女朋友，做人有啲要求，唔好無嚟性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就你，比你揀都要比你話我無性格，你咪去搵個死港女虐待下你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二個ex話我對佢太好，比足夠自由度，又做足女朋友應該做嘅野，不過佢自己做得唔好，所以覺得對我唔住，決定搵個差啲嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到我頭都大埋，因為女朋友對自己太好，所以頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵個會虐待你地嘅女人啦，我會考慮虐待下一個男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17701882032d6c4bbdf439254fed90ae8afb18d8","tid":346443,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:20:01.000Z","msg":"快點"},{"pid":"be85a8afc23acadd99e269768e91a674b981fb09","tid":346443,"uid":55614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/112025_4f19f1d1d70c3438375e0126725d42c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F112025_4f19f1d1d70c3438375e0126725d42c6.jpg&h=1471648e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff45de957d34c56b95031c158ff986bd4b0f7960","tid":346443,"uid":76242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"咁你鍾意比男人虐待？"},{"pid":"098d09bd7da4bde27c61ce18d5ca2b9d6c755345","tid":346443,"uid":32797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=